.TH "ntfs_perform_write" 9 "ntfs_perform_write" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ntfs_perform_write \- perform buffered write to a file
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "ssize_t" ntfs_perform_write
.BI "(struct file *file "  ","
.BI "struct iov_iter *i "  ","
.BI "loff_t pos "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "file" 12
file to write to
.IP "i" 12
iov_iter with data to write
.IP "pos" 12
byte offset in file at which to begin writing to
